Package lombok.eclipse.agent

Contains the mechanism that instruments eclipse by being loaded as a javaagent.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EclipseLoaderPatcher  
    EclipseLoaderPatcherTransplants
    Contains all the code to be transplanted into eclipse.
    EclipsePatcher
    This is a java-agent that patches some of eclipse's classes so AST Nodes are handed off to Lombok for modification before Eclipse actually uses them to compile, render errors, show code outlines, create auto-completion dialogs, and anything else eclipse does with java code.
